Detailed Description

Structure to hold the BSS ESM Fault data strucutre for event RL_RF_AE_ESMFAULT_SB.

Note
: The Programmable filter Parity error and double bit ECC errors are fatal errors but connected to ESM Group 1 lines, these shuld be treated as fatal errors on the Host . (MSS or DSS in xWR1642, xWR1843 and xWR6843 devices)
